				<td colspan="2"><span>well hey Bud!
<br />

<br />
long time no see.......
<br />

<br />
you are twinking out blayes pretty good....you may not get many answers for your questions...
<br />

<br />
guluvasea's stuff is:
<br />
http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=624036
<br />

<br />
I know you want to keep blayes at lvl 52 for some time to come but i also think you need some FT gear like the earring.  it costs so little nowadays and even just a +1 ft will help you.  I assume you are putting all exp into AA for the time being so you might just increase your natural Cha or Dex.
<br />

<br />
my bard's profile isnt a lot different from yours although your bard will have more hit points than mine by the time you hit lvl 58.  my ac runs a little over 1000 and the attack can get pretty high too when in werewolf form (of which i am normally in most of the time).  I did notice my dexterity is about 30 pts higher which is on purpose.  I am trying to keep it high to reduce missed notes.  not sure if it helps or not.  I have the gear with me, at all times, to kick my charisma up to 200 for those ldons and wear my ss helm for the eye effect and everything seems to go well on the raids i am pulling.
<br />

<br />
get a new breastplate i am thinking... I know you got your epic, grats btw, but i am surprised that the udb didnt drop an SS bp....he normally does you know.
<br />

<br />
and since you are one of the rich and famous, since you farm ornate in solro with blayda and deeply, have you considered farming/buying ornate for blayes?  Run over to the dwarf in pot and see if he will talk to blayes about it.. if he does he will give you the forms (for 500 plat) and you can make it yourself.  Not sure if there is a level restriction but i can tell you i was buying my necro booties and sleeves at level 57 or 58.  you never know.
<br />

<br />
give me a tell sometime and you and me can run over to WW and work on the draconic pauldrons...assuming you have the faction for it  ( i am still kos but dekkon can stil kill those mobs for you).
<br />

<br />
find some new earrings...blood earring of rage is nice... drops in the spit in tactics.
<br />

<br />
see ya bud!
<br />
dekkon</span></td>
